53 CollisionEnvBullet::CollisionEnvBullet(const moveit::core::RobotModelConstPtr& model, double padding, double scale)
54  : CollisionEnv(model, padding, scale)
55 {
56  // request notifications about changes to new world
57  observer_handle_ = getWorld()->addObserver(boost::bind(&CollisionEnvBullet::notifyObjectChange, this, _1, _2));
58 
59  for (const std::pair<const std::string, urdf::LinkSharedPtr>& link : robot_model_->getURDF()->links_)
60  {
61  addLinkAsCollisionObject(link.second);
62  }
63 }

113 void CollisionEnvBullet::checkSelfCollisionHelper(const CollisionRequest& req, CollisionResult& res,
114  const moveit::core::RobotState& state,
115  const AllowedCollisionMatrix* acm) const
116 {
117  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> guard(collision_env_mutex_);
118 
119  std::vector<collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr> cows;
120  addAttachedOjects(state, cows);
121 
122  if (req.distance)
123  {
124  manager_->setContactDistanceThreshold(MAX_DISTANCE_MARGIN);
125  }
126 
127  for (const collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr& cow : cows)
128  {
129  manager_->addCollisionObject(cow);
130  manager_->setCollisionObjectsTransform(
131  cow->getName(), state.getAttachedBody(cow->getName())->getGlobalCollisionBodyTransforms()[0]);
132  }
133 
134  // updating link positions with the current robot state
135  for (const std::string& link : active_)
136  {
137  manager_->setCollisionObjectsTransform(link, state.getCollisionBodyTransform(link, 0));
138  }
139 
140  manager_->contactTest(res, req, acm, true);
141 
142  for (const collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr& cow : cows)
143  {
144  manager_->removeCollisionObject(cow->getName());
145  }
146 }

176 void CollisionEnvBullet::checkRobotCollisionHelper(const CollisionRequest& req, CollisionResult& res,
177  const moveit::core::RobotState& state,
178  const AllowedCollisionMatrix* acm) const
179 {
180  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> guard(collision_env_mutex_);
181 
182  if (req.distance)
183  {
184  manager_->setContactDistanceThreshold(MAX_DISTANCE_MARGIN);
185  }
186 
187  std::vector<collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr> attached_cows;
188  addAttachedOjects(state, attached_cows);
189  updateTransformsFromState(state, manager_);
190 
191  for (const collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr& cow : attached_cows)
192  {
193  manager_->addCollisionObject(cow);
194  manager_->setCollisionObjectsTransform(
195  cow->getName(), state.getAttachedBody(cow->getName())->getGlobalCollisionBodyTransforms()[0]);
196  }
197 
198  manager_->contactTest(res, req, acm, false);
199 
200  for (const collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr& cow : attached_cows)
201  {
202  manager_->removeCollisionObject(cow->getName());
203  }
204 }

206 void CollisionEnvBullet::checkRobotCollisionHelperCCD(const CollisionRequest& req, CollisionResult& res,
207  const moveit::core::RobotState& state1,
208  const moveit::core::RobotState& state2,
209  const AllowedCollisionMatrix* acm) const
210 {
211  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> guard(collision_env_mutex_);
212 
213  std::vector<collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr> attached_cows;
214  addAttachedOjects(state1, attached_cows);
215 
216  for (const collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr& cow : attached_cows)
217  {
218  manager_CCD_->addCollisionObject(cow);
219  manager_CCD_->setCastCollisionObjectsTransform(
220  cow->getName(), state1.getAttachedBody(cow->getName())->getGlobalCollisionBodyTransforms()[0],
221  state2.getAttachedBody(cow->getName())->getGlobalCollisionBodyTransforms()[0]);
222  }
223 
224  for (const std::string& link : active_)
225  {
226  manager_CCD_->setCastCollisionObjectsTransform(link, state1.getCollisionBodyTransform(link, 0),
227  state2.getCollisionBodyTransform(link, 0));
228  }
229 
230  manager_CCD_->contactTest(res, req, acm, false);
231 
232  for (const collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr& cow : attached_cows)
233  {
234  manager_CCD_->removeCollisionObject(cow->getName());
235  }
236 }

250 void CollisionEnvBullet::addToManager(const World::Object* obj)
251 {
252  std::vector<collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectType> collision_object_types;
253 
254  for (const shapes::ShapeConstPtr& shape : obj->shapes_)
255  {
256  if (shape->type == shapes::MESH)
257  collision_object_types.push_back(collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectType::CONVEX_HULL);
258  else
259  collision_object_types.push_back(collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectType::USE_SHAPE_TYPE);
260  }
261 
262  auto cow = std::make_shared<collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapper>(
263  obj->id_, collision_detection::BodyType::WORLD_OBJECT, obj->shapes_, obj->global_shape_poses_,
264  collision_object_types, false);
265 
266  manager_->addCollisionObject(cow);
267  manager_CCD_->addCollisionObject(cow->clone());
268 }

270 void CollisionEnvBullet::updateManagedObject(const std::string& id)
271 {
272  if (getWorld()->hasObject(id))
273  {
274  auto it = getWorld()->find(id);
275  if (manager_->hasCollisionObject(id))
276  {
277  manager_->removeCollisionObject(id);
278  manager_CCD_->removeCollisionObject(id);
279  addToManager(it->second.get());
280  }
281  else
282  {
283  addToManager(it->second.get());
284  }
285  }
286  else
287  {
288  if (manager_->hasCollisionObject(id))
289  {
290  manager_->removeCollisionObject(id);
291  manager_CCD_->removeCollisionObject(id);
292  }
293  }
294 }

296 void CollisionEnvBullet::setWorld(const WorldPtr& world)
297 {
298  if (world == getWorld())
299  return;
300 
301  // turn off notifications about old world
302  getWorld()->removeObserver(observer_handle_);
303 
304  CollisionEnv::setWorld(world);
305 
306  // request notifications about changes to new world
307  observer_handle_ = getWorld()->addObserver(boost::bind(&CollisionEnvBullet::notifyObjectChange, this, _1, _2));
308 
309  // get notifications any objects already in the new world
310  getWorld()->notifyObserverAllObjects(observer_handle_, World::CREATE);
311 }
312 
313 void CollisionEnvBullet::notifyObjectChange(const ObjectConstPtr& obj, World::Action action)
314 {
315  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> guard(collision_env_mutex_);
316  if (action == World::DESTROY)
317  {
318  manager_->removeCollisionObject(obj->id_);
319  manager_CCD_->removeCollisionObject(obj->id_);
320  }
321  else
322  {
323  updateManagedObject(obj->id_);
324  }
325 }

327 void CollisionEnvBullet::addAttachedOjects(const moveit::core::RobotState& state,
328  std::vector<collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr>& cows) const
329 {
330  std::vector<const moveit::core::AttachedBody*> attached_bodies;
331  state.getAttachedBodies(attached_bodies);
332 
333  for (const moveit::core::AttachedBody*& body : attached_bodies)
334  {
335  const EigenSTL::vector_Isometry3d& attached_body_transform = body->getGlobalCollisionBodyTransforms();
336 
337  std::vector<collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectType> collision_object_types(
338  attached_body_transform.size(), collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectType::USE_SHAPE_TYPE);
339 
340  try
341  {
342  collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr cow(new collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapper(
343  body->getName(), collision_detection::BodyType::ROBOT_ATTACHED, body->getShapes(), attached_body_transform,
344  collision_object_types, body->getTouchLinks()));
345  cows.push_back(cow);
346  }
347  catch (std::exception&)
348  {
349  ROS_ERROR_STREAM_NAMED("collision_detetction.bullet",
350  "Not adding " << body->getName() << " due to bad arguments.");
351  }
352  }
353 }

355 void CollisionEnvBullet::updatedPaddingOrScaling(const std::vector<std::string>& links)
356 {
357  for (const std::string& link : links)
358  {
359  if (robot_model_->getURDF()->links_.find(link) != robot_model_->getURDF()->links_.end())
360  {
361  addLinkAsCollisionObject(robot_model_->getURDF()->links_[link]);
362  }
363  else
364  {
365  ROS_ERROR_NAMED("collision_detection.bullet", "Updating padding or scaling for unknown link: '%s'", link.c_str());
366  }
367  }
368 }

370 void CollisionEnvBullet::updateTransformsFromState(
371  const moveit::core::RobotState& state, const collision_detection_bullet::BulletDiscreteBVHManagerPtr& manager) const
372 {
373  // updating link positions with the current robot state
374  for (const std::string& link : active_)
375  {
376  // select the first of the transformations for each link (composed of multiple shapes...)
377  manager->setCollisionObjectsTransform(link, state.getCollisionBodyTransform(link, 0));
378  }

381 void CollisionEnvBullet::addLinkAsCollisionObject(const urdf::LinkSharedPtr& link)
382 {
383  if (!link->collision_array.empty())
384  {
385  const std::vector<urdf::CollisionSharedPtr>& col_array =
386  link->collision_array.empty() ? std::vector<urdf::CollisionSharedPtr>(1, link->collision) :
387  link->collision_array;
388 
389  std::vector<shapes::ShapeConstPtr> shapes;
390  collision_detection_bullet::AlignedVector<Eigen::Isometry3d> shape_poses;
391  std::vector<collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectType> collision_object_types;
392 
393  for (const auto& i : col_array)
394  {
395  if (i && i->geometry)
396  {
397  shapes::ShapePtr shape = collision_detection_bullet::constructShape(i->geometry.get());
398 
399  if (shape)
400  {
401  if (fabs(getLinkScale(link->name) - 1.0) >= std::numeric_limits<double>::epsilon() ||
402  fabs(getLinkPadding(link->name)) >= std::numeric_limits<double>::epsilon())
403  {
404  shape->scaleAndPadd(getLinkScale(link->name), getLinkPadding(link->name));
405  }
406 
407  shapes.push_back(shape);
408  shape_poses.push_back(collision_detection_bullet::urdfPose2Eigen(i->origin));
409 
410  if (shape->type == shapes::MESH)
411  {
412  collision_object_types.push_back(collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectType::CONVEX_HULL);
413  }
414  else
415  {
416  collision_object_types.push_back(collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectType::USE_SHAPE_TYPE);
417  }
418  }
419  }
420  }
421 
422  if (manager_->hasCollisionObject(link->name))
423  {
424  manager_->removeCollisionObject(link->name);
425  manager_CCD_->removeCollisionObject(link->name);
426  }
427 
428  try
429  {
430  collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr cow(new collision_detection_bullet::CollisionObjectWrapper(
431  link->name, collision_detection::BodyType::ROBOT_LINK, shapes, shape_poses, collision_object_types, true));
432  manager_->addCollisionObject(cow);
433  manager_CCD_->addCollisionObject(cow->clone());
434  active_.push_back(cow->getName());
435  }
436  catch (std::exception&)
437  {
438  ROS_ERROR_STREAM_NAMED("collision_detetction.bullet", "Not adding " << link->name << " due to bad arguments.");
439  }
440  }
441 }
